[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returned</st> <st data-num=\"0413 01004\">home</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">safely</st> to <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "the <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">prophet</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03058\" class=\"\">Jehu</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02607\" class=\"\">Hanani</st> <st data-num=\"03318 0413\">confronted</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">him</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st>, \u201cIs it right to <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">help</st> the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st> and <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">be an ally</st> of those who <st data-num=\"08130\" class=\"\">oppose</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>?<n id=\"3\" /> Because you have done <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"06440 03068\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"07110\" class=\"\">angry</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">with</st> you!<n id=\"4\" />",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"061\" class=\"\">Nevertheless</st> you have <st data-num=\"04672 05973\">done</st> some <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">things</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> you <st data-num=\"03588 01197\">removed</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0842\" class=\"\">Asherah poles</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>, and you were <st data-num=\"03559 03824\">determined</st> to <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">follow</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lived</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> He <st data-num=\"07725 03318\">went out</st> among the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> from <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hill country</st> of <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> and <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">encouraged</st> them <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> follow<n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">appointed</st> <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judges</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">throughout</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> and in <st data-num=\"05892 05892\">each</st> of the <st data-num=\"01219\" class=\"\">fortified</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judges</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Be careful</st> <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> you are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judging</st> for <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">men</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">but</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, who will be <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you when you make <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judicial</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">decisions</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06258 01961 06343 05921\">Respect</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">careful decisions</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"0369 05973\">disapproves of</st> <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">injustice</st>, <st data-num=\"04856 06440\">partiality</st>, and <st data-num=\"04727 07810\">bribery</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">In <st data-num=\"01571 03389\">Jerusalem</st> <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">appointed</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">some</st> <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st>, <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>, and <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">family</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st> to <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judge</st> on behalf of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><n id=\"1\" /> and to settle <st data-num=\"07379\" class=\"\">disputes</st> among the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"06680 05921 0559\">commanded</st> them: \u201c<st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">Carry out</st> your <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">duties</st> with <st data-num=\"03374\" class=\"\">respect</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, with <st data-num=\"0530\" class=\"\">honesty</st>, and with <st data-num=\"08003\" class=\"\">pure</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">motives</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">Whenever</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">countrymen</st> who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> a <st data-num=\"07379 0834\">case</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">before</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> (<st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">whether</st> it involves a <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">violent</st> <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">crime</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">or</st> other matters related to the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>, <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">commandments</st>, <st data-num=\"02706\" class=\"\">rules</st>, and <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">regulations</st>), <st data-num=\"02094\" class=\"\">warn</st> them that they must <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">sin</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. If you fail to do so, God will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"07110\" class=\"\">angry</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">with</st> you <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">colleagues</st>, but if you <st data-num=\"03541 06213\">obey</st>, you will <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">free</st> <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">of guilt</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "19",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Take note</st>, <st data-num=\"0568\" class=\"\">Amariah</st> the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">chief</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> will <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">oversee</st><n id=\"1\" /> you in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">matter</st> pertaining to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"02069\" class=\"\">Zebadiah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"03458\" class=\"\">Ishmael</st>, the <st data-num=\"05057\" class=\"\">leader</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">matter</st> pertaining to the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. The <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> will serve as <st data-num=\"07860\" class=\"\">officials</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you. <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">Act</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">courageously</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and may the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">those who do well</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  }
]